<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
      xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
      xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
      xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
      i18n:domain="vk.bulkmove"
      metal:use-macro="context/main_template/macros/master">
<body>

  <metal:main fill-slot="main">

    <div tal:condition="python: not view.valid">

        <h1 class="documentFirstHeading">CSV-Datei hochladen</h1>

        <p class="documentDescription">
           Wählen sie eine csv-Datei mit Informationen zu den zu verschiebenden Inhalten aus.
        </p>

       <form
            name="upload"
            method="post"
            enctype="multipart/form-data"
            class="pat-formunloadalert"
            tal:attributes="action request/URL">

            <div
                class="field">
                <input
                    type="file"
                    name="instructions_file"
                    id="instructions_file"
                />
            </div>

            <div class="plone-btn-group">
                <input
                    type="submit"
                    name="form.button.Upload"
                    class="plone-btn plone-btn-success save"
                    value="Hochladen"
                    i18n:attributes="value" />

                <input
                    type="submit"
                    name="form.button.Cancel"
                    class="plone-btn plone-btn-default cancel"
                    value="Abbrechen"
                    i18n:attributes="value" />
            </div>
        </form>

    </div>

    <div tal:condition="python:view.valid and not view.move_completed">
        <h1 class="documentFirstHeading">Inhalte verschieben</h1>

        <p>
            Folgende Operationen wurden eingelesen. Nicht vorhandene Objekte oder Objekte falschen Typs sind rot gekennzeichnet:
        </p>

        <table>
            <tr>
                <th>source</th>
                <th>target</th>
            </tr>
        
            <tr tal:repeat="action view/actions">
                <td tal:condition="python:action['source_ok']" tal:attributes="style string:color:green;" tal:content="action/source">/x/y/z</td>
                <td tal:condition="python:not action['source_ok']" tal:attributes="style string:color:red;" tal:content="action/source">/x/y/z</td>

                <td tal:condition="python:action['target_ok']" tal:attributes="style string:color:green;" tal:content="action/target">/a/b/c</td>
                <td tal:condition="python:not action['target_ok']" tal:attributes="style string:color:red;" tal:content="action/target">/a/b/c</td>
            </tr>

        </table>
        <br/>
        <p>
            Die nachfolgend aufgeführten Verschiebe-Operationen werden durchgeführt:
        </p>

        <table>
            <tr>
                <th>source</th>
                <th>target</th>
            </tr>
        
            <tr tal:repeat="action view/valid_actions">
                <td tal:attributes="style string:color:green;" tal:content="action/source">/x/y/z</td>
                <td tal:attributes="style string:color:green;" tal:content="action/target">/a/b/c</td>
                
            </tr>

        </table>
        <br/>
        <form
            name="move"
            method="post"
            enctype="multipart/form-data"
            class="pat-formunloadalert"
            tal:attributes="action request/URL">

                <input
                    type="hidden"
                    name="valid_actions_dict"
                    tal:attributes="value view/valid_actions"
                    />

            <div class="plone-btn-group">
                <input
                    type="submit"
                    name="form.button.Move"
                    class="plone-btn plone-btn-success save"
                    value="Verschieben"
                    i18n:attributes="value" />

                <input
                    type="submit"
                    name="form.button.Cancel"
                    class="plone-btn plone-btn-default cancel"
                    value="Cancel"
                    i18n:attributes="value" />
            </div>
        </form>

    </div>

    <div tal:condition="python:view.valid and view.move_completed">
        Es wurden <span tal:content="python: len(view.valid_actions)"/> Objekte verschoben.
    </div> 

  </metal:main>
</body>
</html>
